column5: EYES Didnt pop off the PR or ER but admit bottom fishers in the 80s or below could make for yet another swing up to a buck or so for some decent beer money Still got to deal with delisting and possible reverse split and still got folks hanging hopes on Williams perpetual buys but thats been going on for a long time now Also not expecting theyll have anything new at the conference but some longs will say different albeit with nothing to back it up GLTA
